"'''Planets'''" is a department within the [[Star Wars: Darth Vader (magazine)|''Star Wars: Darth Vader'']] magazine published by [[De Agostini]]. Like the "[[Starships and Equipment]]" section, "Planets" is only included in the French and Spanish versions of the magazine, and is excluded from other language versions.

